atement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Controversy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deportation%20proposal%20has%20been%20mired%20in%20controversy%20and%20legal%20battles%20since%20Boris%20Johnson%20unveiled%20it%20when%20he%20was%20prime%20minister%20in%202022.%20So%20far%2C%20no%20migrants%20have%20been%20sent%20to%20Rwanda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20November%2C%20the%20UK%20Supreme%20Court%20declared%20the%20policy%20unlawful%20and%20Rishi%20Sunak%20hopes%20the%20new%20legislation%20will%20override%20legal%20concerns%20and%20fulfill%20his%20pledge%20to%20stop%20people%20arriving%20across%20the%20Channel%20in%20small%20boats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERwanda%2C%20a%20tiny%20nation%20of%2013%20million%20people%2C%20claims%20to%20being%20one%20of%20the%20most%20stable%20countries%20in%20Africa.%20But%20rights%20groups%20accuse%20veteran%20President%20Paul%20Kagame%20of%20ruling%20in%20a%20climate%20of%20fear%2C%20stifling%20dissent%20and%20free%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20no%20deportations%20taking%20place%2C%20Britain%20has%20already%20paid%20Rwanda%20240%20million%20pounds.%20While%20Britain%20hopes%20to%20send%20thousands%20of%20migrants%2C%20at%20the%20moment%20Rwanda%20only%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20take%20a%20few%20hundred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Was%20Britain's%20Rwanda%20Plan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rwanda%20scheme%2C%20agreed%20in%20April%202022%20by%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Boris%20Johnson%2C%20is%20designed%20to%20deter%20migrants%20from%20coming%20to%20Britain%20illegally%20and%20break%20the%20business%20model%20of%20people%20smugglers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20plan%2C%20anyone%20who%20arrived%20in%20Britain%20illegally%20after%20January%201%2C%202022%2C%20faced%20being%20sent%20to%20Rwanda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20first%20deportation%20flight%20in%20June%202022%20was%20blocked%20by%20European%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20Supreme%20Court%20then%20unanimously%20upheld%20a%20ruling%20that%20the%20scheme%20was%20unlawful%20because%20migrants%20were%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20sent%20back%20to%20their%20homelands%20or%20to%20other%20countries%20where%20they%20would%20be%20at%20risk%20of%20mistreatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20Rishi%20Sunak's%20Rwanda%20Bill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20the%20issues%20raised%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20Rishi%20Sunak%20agreed%20a%20new%20treaty%20with%20Rwanda%20that%20seeks%20to%20prevent%20anyone%20from%20being%20sent%20anywhere%20else%20other%20than%20back%20to%20Britain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20bill%20compels%20judges%20to%20regard%20the%20east%20African%20nation%20as%20a%20safe%20third%20country%20and%20gives%20ministers%20the%20power%20to%20disregard%20sections%20of%20international%20and%20British%20human%20rights%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20legal%20experts%2C%20however%2C%20say%20as%20the%20bill%20stands%2C%20Britain%20would%20still%20be%20bound%20by%20findings%20of%20the%20European%20Court%20of%20Human%20Rights%20which%20could%20again%20issue%20injunctions%20to%20block%20deportation%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20becoming%20prime%20minister%20in%20October%20last%20year%2C%20Sunak%20made%20%26quot%3Bstop%20the%20boats%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20his%20top%20five%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year%20Sunak%20said%20he%20had%20met%20a%20pledge%20to%20clear%20a%20so-called%20'legacy%20backlog'%20of%2092%2C000%20asylum%20claims%20which%20were%20made%20before%20a%20June%202022%20change%20in%20immigration%20law%2C%20although%20figures%20show%20about%20100%2C000%20applications%20still%20remain%20to%20be%20decided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713859620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F6om28o0g_rishi-sunak-reuters_625x300_12_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frishi-sunak-rwanda-plan-explained-wh