314%2Fputin-secret-jamming-weapon-tobol-behind-flights-attacked-russia%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Sun%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20carrying%20images%20of%20a%20large%20satellite%20dish%20mounted%20on%20the%20ground%20at%20the%20Kaliningrad%20base%20claiming%20that%20it%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Tobol%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20official%20confirmation%20if%20it%20indeed%20is%20the%20Russian%20secret%20weapon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outlet%20also%20said%20that%20there%20are%2010%20such%20devices%20across%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20jamming%20satellite%20signals%2C%20it%20can%20protect%20Russian%20bases%20from%20becoming%20the%20targets%20of%20NATO's%20missiles%20by%20confusing%20the%20weapons.%20However%2C%20it%20can't%20stop%20missiles%20from%20exploding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20jamming%20works%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnational-security%2F2023%2F04%2F18%2Fdiscord-leaks-starlink-ukraine%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20it%20happens%20in%20two%20ways%3A%20In%20space%2C%20by%20targeting%20the%20satellites%20directly%2C%20and%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20where%20weapons%20can%20target%20receivers.%20In%20the%20first%20type%20of%20jamming%2C%20a%20signal%20is%20blended%20with%20the%20original%20broadcast%2C%20which%20distorts%20the%20information%20all%20the%20users%20of%20that%20satellite%20receive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outlet%20quoted%20researcher%20Bart%20Hendrickx%20as%20saying%20that%20Tobol%20works%20in%20this%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%20this%20year%2C%20Erik%20Kannike%2C%20of%20Estonia-based%20software%20company%20SensusQ%2C%20had%20claimed%20on%20X%20that%20widespread%20GPS%20disruptions%20plaguing%20NATO%20assets%20is%20Tobol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20countries%2C%20including%20Finland%2C%20Poland%20and%20Sweden%2C%20have%20reported%20GPS%20disturbances%20in%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Frussia-electronic-warfare-gps-jamming-nato-finland-poland-sweden-kaliningrad-ukraine-1863096%5C%22%3Eas%20per%20%3Cem%3ENewsweek%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Speaking%20to%20Swedish%20media%20about%20it%2C%20Sweden's%20Lieutenant%20Colonel%20Joakim%20Paasikivi%20said%20the%20interference%20is%20a%20result%20of%20%26quot%3BRussian%20influence%20activities%20or%20so-called%20hybrid%20warfare%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20experimented%20with%20the%20Tobol%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20disrupt%20Starlink%20transmissions%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20The%20Washington%20Post%20reported%20in%20April%202023%2C%20citing%20a%20classified%20US%20intelligence%20report.%20Ukraine's%20access%20to%20satellite%20networks%20like%20Starlink%20are%20critical%20to%20many%20of%20its%20operations%20and%20communications.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713855960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fjmdfkc3_tobol-system_625x300_23_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fall-about-tobol-russias-secret-weapon-linked-to-jamming-of-planes-signals-5503632%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tobol%20electronic%20warfare%20system%20was%20previously%20linked%20to%20jamming%20of%20signals%20of%20ships%20on%20NATO's%20eastern%20flank.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fall-about-tobol-russias-secret-weapon-linked-to-jamming-of-planes-signals-5503632%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fall-about-tobol-russias-secret-weapon-linked-to-jamming-of-planes-signals-5503632%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fall-about-tobol-russias-secret-weapon-linked-to-jamming-of-planes-signals-5503632%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Listening%20to%20Hanuman%20Chalisa%20becomes%20crime%20under%20Congress%3A%20PM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A17138558950