BrahMos%20to%20the%20Philippines%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fbrahmos-supersonic-cruise-missile-news%5C%22%3EBrahMos%3C%2Fa%3E%20Aerospace%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%20an%20Indo-Russian%20joint%20venture.%20Apart%20from%20two%20missile%20launchers%2C%20a%20radar%20and%20a%20command-and-control%20centre%2C%20the%20pact%20includes%20an%20integrated%20logistics%20support%20package%20and%20training%20for%20those%20manning%20the%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20major%20boost%20for%20Delhi-Manila%20ties.%20But%20the%20significance%20of%20this%20goes%20beyond%20the%20bilateral%20as%20India%20seeks%20to%20enhance%20its%20presence%20as%20a%20credible%20defence%20partner%20in%20Southeast%20Asia%20and%20the%20wider%20Indo-Pacific.%20Moreover%2C%20this%20also%20showcases%20the%20growing%20salience%20of%20India's%20domestic%20defence%20manufacturing%20base%2C%20which%20has%20been%20coming%20into%20its%20own%20as%20part%20of%20the%20wider%20'Make%20in%20India'%20programme%20launched%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPhilippines%20Is%20Building%20New%20Partnerships%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20President%20Ferdinand%20Marcos%20Jr.%2C%20the%20Philippines%20is%20recalibrating%20its%20foreign%20policy%20priorities%20and%20moving%20away%20from%20the%20China-dominated%20outlook%20of%20his%20predecessor%20Rodrigo%20Duterte.%20Facing%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fphilippines-summons-chinese-envoy-over-aggressive-actions-by-china-coast-guard-in-south-china-sea-5307185%5C%22%3Eaggressive%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Manila%20is%20reaching%20out%20and%20building%20substantive%20new%20partnerships%20that%20can%20give%20it%20enough%20space%20to%20manoeuvre.%20Manila%20is%20pursuing%20a%20multi-aligned%20foreign%20policy%20strategy%2C%20prioritising%20the%20strengthening%20and%20diversification%20of%20security%20and%20economic%20ties%20with%20both%20traditional%20and%20non-traditional%20allies.%20This%20approach%20is%20aimed%20at%20increasing%20its%20strategic%20options%20in%20a%20fluid%20regional%20and%20global%20geopolitical%20environment%2C%20particularly%20in%20response%20to%20increasing%20pressures%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffirst-us-japan-philippines-summit-to-boost-defence-ties-china-reacts-5398745%5C%22%3EBeijing%20in%20the%20West%20Philippine%20Sea%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Though%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffirst-us-japan-philippines-summit-to-boost-defence-ties-china-reacts-5398745%5C%22%3EUnited%20States%20continues%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20the%20primary%20security%20partner%20for%20the%20Philippines%2C%20it%20has%20now%20become%20imperative%20for%20Manila%20to%20broaden%20the%20ambit%20of%20its%20external%20partnerships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderlining%20the%20acquisition%20of%20BrahMos%20cruise%20missiles%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20game-changer%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Philippines%20views%20them%20as%20essential%20in%20pushing%20back%20against%20Chinese%20expansionist%20claims%20in%20the%20West%20Philippine%20Sea%20by%20bolstering%20the%20nation's%20coastal%20defence.%20Delhi%20and%20Manila%20are%20casting%20a%20relook%20at%20each%20other%20beyond%20defence%20transactions%20too.%20During%20his%20visit%20to%20Manila%20last%20month%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20stated%20that%20prosperity%20in%20the%20region%20is%20%26quot%3Bbest%20served%20by%20staunch%20adherence%20to%20a%20rules-based%20order%26quot%3B%2C%20highlighting%20the%201982%20UN%20Convention%20on%20the%20Law%20of%20the%20Sea%20(UNCLOS)%20as%20a%20foundational%20aspect%20of%20this%20approach.%20He%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Ball%20parties%20must%20adhere%20to%20%5BUNCLOS%5D%20in%20its%20entirety%2C%20both%20in%20letter%20and%20in%20spirit%26quot%3B%20and%20reiterated%20%26quot%3BIndia's%20support%20to%20the%20Philippines%20for%20upholding%20its%20national%20sovereignty%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Aim%20Of%20Expanding%20Its%20Indo-Pacific%20Role%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20new%20robust%20defence%20policy%20has%20been%20announced%20by%20Manila%20in%20recent%20months%20and%20it%20is%20enhancing%20defence%20ties%20with%20like-minded%20partners.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Manila%2C%20Washington%20and%20Tokyo%20announced%20joint%20drills%20in%20their%20first-ever%20trilateral%20summit%20and%20there%20are%20plans%20to%20negotiate%20a%20new%20status%20of%20visiting%20forces%20agreement%20with%20New%20Zealand.%20A%20strong%20partnership%20with%20India%20will%20also%20be%20an%20important%20aspect%20of%20this%20new%20foreign%20policy%20matrix%20of%20Manila%20as%20New%20Delhi%20too%20seeks%20a%20greater%20role%20and%20voice%20in%20the%20wider%20Indo-Pacific.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20role%20as%20a%20net%20security%20provider%20in%20the%20region%20is%20being%20crafted%20slowly%20but%20surely%20and%20India's%20defence%20supplies%20certainly%20enhance%20its%20credibility%20in%20this%20realm.%20Many%20regional%20players%20are%20looking%20at%20alternatives%20to%20the%20dominance%20of%20China%20and%20the%20US%20in%20the%20regional%20security%20calculus.%20India's%20naval%20presence%20and%20defence%20cooperation%20agreements%20extend%20its%20influence%20across%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20and%20beyond.%20By%20engaging%20in%20joint%20exercises%2C%20capacity-building%20programmes%2C%20and%20humanitarian%20assistance%20missions%2C%20India%20asserts%20its%20commitment%20to%20fostering%20a%20secure%20and%20prosperous%20Indo-Pacific%20region.%20New%20Delhi%20is%20an%20attractive%20partner%20given%20its%20history%20of%20defending%20strategic%20autonomy%2C%20but%20there%20have%20always%20been%20questions%20about%20its%20ability%20to%20deliver.%20The%20BrahMos%20delivery%20is%20an%20important%20turning%20point%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20another%20aspect%20of%20the%20BrahMos%20missiles%20that%20is%20quite%20interesting.%20This%20missile%20is%20also%20a%20statement%20on%20close%20defence%20ties%20between%20Delhi%20and%20Moscow%20-%20the%20result%20of%20a%20joint%20venture%20between%20India's%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20(DRDO)%20and%20Russia's%20NPO%20Mashinostroyeniya.%20And%20it%20has%20been%20sold%20to%20Manila%2C%20a%20close%20ally%20of%20the%20US%2C%20to%20manage%20the%20threat%20from%20China%2C%20an%20emerging%20strategic%20partner%20of%20Russia.%20New%20Delhi's%20unique%20role%20in%20contemporary%20geopolitics%20is%20reflected%20in%20this%20strange%20equation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEvolving%20Defence%20Priorities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sale%20of%20BrahMos%20also%20showcases%20how%20India's%20defence%20exports%20have%20surged%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20bolstered%20by%20the%20government's%20'Make%20in%20India'%20initiative%20that%20is%20aimed%20at%20enhancing%20domestic%20defence%20production.%20By%20promoting%20indigenous%20capabilities%20and%20leveraging%20its%20growing%20defence%20industry%2C%20India%20aims%20to%20become%20a%20significant%20player%20in%20the%20global%20defence%20market%20from%20the%20world's%20largest%20arms%20importer%2C%20while%20simultaneously%20strengthening%20its%20national%20security%20and%20economic%20resilience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificant%20though%20it%20is%2C%20this%20one%20sale%20of%20BrahMos%20is%20neither%20going%20to%20resolve%20the%20defence%20challenges%20of%20Manila%20nor%20is%20it%20going%20to%20dramatically%20alter%20New%20Delhi's%20security%20profile%20in%20the%20region.%20But%20it%20highlights%20how%20Indian%20defence%20priorities%20are%20evolving%20rapidly%20amidst%20a%20wider%20regional%20flux.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%5BHarsh%20V.%20Pant%20is%20a%20Professor%20of%20International%20Relations%20at%20King's%20College%20London.%20His%20most%20recent%20books%20include%20'India%20and%20the%20Gulf%3A%20Theoretical%20Perspectives%20and%20Policy%20Shifts'%20(Cambridge%20University%20Press)%20and%20'Politics%20and%20Geopolitics%3A%20Decoding%20India's%20Neighbourhood%20Challenge'%20(Rupa)%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713853380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-05%2Fbrahmos_650x400_81493840841.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbrahmos-for-philippines-indias-symbolic-win-in-the-choppy-indo-pacific-5503259%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20delivery%20of%20the%20first%20BrahMos%20missile%20to%20the%20Philippines%20highlights%20how%20Indian%20defence%20priorities%20are%20evolving%20rapidly%20amidst%20a%20wider%20regional%20flux.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbrahmos-for-philippines-indias-symbolic-win-in-the-choppy-indo-pacific-5503259%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Australian%20Porn%20Star%20Claims%20Her%20Ex%20Pretended%20To%20Have%20Cancer%20To%20Cheat%20On%20Her%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20Australian%20adult%20star%20has%20claimed%20her%20ex-boyfriend%20pretended%20to%20have%20cancer%20so%20that%20he%20could%20cheat%20on%20her%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F04%2F22%2Flifestyle%2Fmy-ex-shaved-his-head-and-pretended-to-have-cancer-to-cheat-with-another-woman%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%20Speaking%20on%20a%20podcast%2C%C2%A0Hayley%20Davies%20said%20the%20man%20even%20shaved%20his%20head%20to%20make%20his%20lie%20more%20convincing.%20''My%20ex%20lied%20about%20having%20cancer%20so%20he%20could%20have%20a%20whole%20other%20girlfriend%20and%20multiple%20side%20girlfriends%2C''%20she%20said%20during%20a%20recent%20episode%20of%20an%20adult%20entertainment%20interview%20podcast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20model%20who%20was%20born%20in%20New%20Zealand%20but%20grew%20up%20in%20Australia%2C%20revealed%20that%20at%20first%2C%20her%20ex%20claimed%20to%20have%20bone%20cancer%2C%20but%20then%20changed%20his%20story%2C%20claiming%20that%20it%20was%20skin%20cancer.%20She%20further%20grew%20even%20more%20suspicious%20when%20her%20ex%20stopped%20sending%20her%20regular%20video%20updates%20of%20his%20various%20activities%2C%20which%20he%20used%20to%20do%20before.%20When%20she%20asked%20him%20what%20he%20was%20up%20to%2C%20he%20claimed%20he%20was%20with%20a%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20looked%20at%20the%20camera%20roll%20on%20his%20phone%2C%20she%20found%20pictures%20of%20him%20from%20the%20night%20before.%20''I%20see%20the%20photos%20of%20him%20that%20night%20with%20another%20girl.%20Then%20I%20saw%20a%20message%20come%20through%2C%20so%20I%20opened%20it%20and%20it's%2C%20like%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20love%20you%2C%20babe.'%E2%80%9D%20And%20I%20reply%20and%20I'm%2C%20like%2C%20%E2%80%98Who%20are%20you%3F'%20and%20she's%2C%20like%2C%20%E2%80%98What%3F'%20because%20I'm%20replying%20from%20his%20phone%2C''%20Ms%C2%A0Davies%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20woman%20immediately%20called%20her%20up%20and%20the%20two%20talked%20about%20how%20their%20boyfriend%20was%C2%A0lying%20to%20them.%20''She%20had%20no%20idea%20he%20had%20cancer.%20They%20had%20been%20together%20longer%2C%20and%20she%20was%20the%20main%20one%20%E2%80%93%20the%20one%20that%20had%20met%20the%20family%20and%20all%20that%2C''%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20she%20put%20the%20phone%20down%2C%20Ms%20Davies%20broke%20up%20with%20the%20man%20on%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20adult%20star%2C%20who%20makes%20around%20%2430%2C000%20a%20month%20from%20an%20adult%20modelling%20subscription%20site%2C%20said%20that%20her%20jealous%20ex%20recently%20messaged%20her%20on%20TikTok%20demanding%20money.%20He%20claimed%20she%20wouldn't%20be%20successful%20if%20it%20weren't%20for%20a%20''viral%20TikT''%20video%20they'd%20made%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20refused%20his%20demands%20and%20commented%20that%20when%20they%20had%20been%20together%2C%20he%20had%20told%20her%20that%20he%20was%20really%20rich%2C%20and%20owned%20multiple%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713853260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F24gamsd8_hayley-davies_625x300_23_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Faustralian-adult-star-claims-her-ex-shaved-his-head-pretended-to-have-cancer-to-cheat-on-her-5503215%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Speaking%20on%20a%20podcast%2C%20Hayley%20Davies%20said%20the%20man%20even%20shaved%20his%20head%20to%20make%20his%20lie%20more%20convincing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Faustralian-adult-star-claims-her-ex-shaved-his-head-pretended-to-have-cancer-to-cheat-on-her-5503215%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Faustralian-adult-star-claims-her-ex-shaved-his-head-pretended-to-have-cancer-to-cheat-on-her-5503215%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Faustralian-adult-star-claims-her-ex-shaved-his-head-pretended-to-have-cancer-to-cheat-on-her-5503215%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSuch%20A%20Player%20Of%20No%20Use%26quot%3B%3A%20Sehwag%20Launches%20Scathing%20Attack%20At%20IPL%20Star%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPunjab%20Kings%20continue%20to%20reel%20among%20the%20bottom%20sides%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024%20after%20losing%20yet%20another%20contest%2C%20to%20last%20year's%20runners-up%20Gujarat%20Titans%20on%20Sunday.%20With%20primary%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shikhar%20Dhawan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F737-shikhar-dhawan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShikhar%20Dhawan%3C%2