ews%2Fnaima-khatoon-appointed-as-vice-chancellor-of-aligarh-muslim-university-report-5500290%C2%A0%5C%22%3ENaima%20Khatoon%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20appointed%20as%20the%20Vice%20Chancellor%20of%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%20(AMU).%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20appointed%20Ms%20Khatoon%20after%20receiving%20approval%20from%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%2C%20who%20serves%20as%20the%20Visitor%20of%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20that%2C%20AMU%20has%20also%20become%20the%20third%20central%20university%20to%20have%20a%20woman%20Vice-Chancellor.%20While%20Santishree%20Dhulipudi%20Pandit%20is%20is%20the%20current%20VC%20of%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20Najma%20Akhtar%20completed%20her%20tenure%20as%20the%20Vice-Chancellor%20of%20Jamia%20Millia%20Islamia%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Khatoon%20is%20the%20first%20woman%20to%20be%20appointed%20to%20the%20post%20in%20the%20varsity's%20123-year%20history.%20Begum%20Sultan%20Jahan%20became%20the%20Chancellor%20of%20AMU%20in%201920%2C%20making%20her%20the%20first%20and%20only%20woman%20to%20hold%20the%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ESome%20facts%20about%20Naima%20Khatoon%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Naima%20Khatoon%20started%20her%20professional%20journey%20as%20a%20lecturer%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.amu.ac.in%2Ffaculty%2Fwomen-s-college%2Fnaima-khatoon%5C%22%3EAMU%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20August%201988.%20She%20gradually%20rose%20through%20the%20ranks%2C%20becoming%20an%20Associate%20Professor%20in%20April%201998%20and%20eventually%20a%20Professor%20in%20July%202006.%20She%20served%20as%20the%20Professor%20and%20Chairperson%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Psychology%20before%20being%20appointed%20Principal%20at%20Women's%20College%20in%20July%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20She%20taught%20at%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Rwanda%2C%20Central%20Africa%2C%20for%20an%20academic%20year.%20She%20has%20also%20served%20in%20various%20administrative%20roles%20at%20AMU%20%E2%80%93%20Deputy%20Director%20of%20the%20Residential%20Coaching%20Academy%2C%20Deputy%20Proctor%2C%20and%20Provost%20in%20both%20Indira%20Gandhi%20Hall%20and%20Abdullah%20Hall.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Naima%20Khatoon%20has%20a%20PhD%20degree%20in%20Political%20Psychology.%20She%20conducted%20her%20doctoral%20work%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Developing%20Societies%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20AMU.%20She%20has%20presented%20her%20research%20findings%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Louisville%20(USA)%2C%20the%20University%20of%20Alba%20Iulia%20(Romania)%2C%20Chulalongkorn%20University%20(Bangkok)%2C%20and%20the%20Hollings%20Centre%20in%20both%20Istanbul%20(Turkey)%20and%20Boston%20(USA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Ms%20Khatoon%20is%20also%20a%20writer%20and%20researcher%2C%20having%20authored%2C%20co-authored%2C%20and%20edited%20six%20books%20and%20published%20various%20papers%20in%20several%20national%20and%20international%20journals.%20Her%20areas%20of%20expertise%20are%20clinical%2C%20health%2C%20applied%20social%2C%20and%20spiritual%20Psychology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Naima%20Khatoon%20was%20honoured%20with%20the%20Papa%20Mian%20Padma%20Bhushan%20Best%20Girl%20Award%20for%20all-round%20excellence.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713850920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F1q4t3psg_naima-khatun-_625x300_23_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-naima-khatoon-amus-first-woman-vice-chancellor-in-over-100-years-5502893%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Professor%20Naima%20Khatoon%20has%20been%20appointed%20as%20the%20Vice%20Chancellor%20of%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%20(AMU).%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20appointed%20Ms%20Khatoon%20after%20receiving%20approval%20from%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%2C%20who%20serves%20as%20the%20Visitor%20of%20the%20university.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv