%20them%20that%20she%20had%20scratched%20herself%20on%20metal%20wire%2C%20which%20led%20them%20to%20not%20seek%20medical%20attention.%20However%2C%20two%20months%20later%2C%C2%A0she%20developed%20serious%20symptoms%2C%20including%20fever%2C%20back%20pain%2C%20fatigue%20and%20difficulty%20drinking%20water.%20She%20then%20finally%20told%20her%20mother%C2%A0Roselyn%20Saraspe%20what%20had%20happened%20and%20was%20rushed%20to%20San%20Lazaro%20Hospital%20on%20April%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20mother%20said%20she%20%26quot%3Bfelt%20her%20heart%20being%20crushed%26quot%3B%20when%20she%20saw%20her%20daughter's%20condition%20rapidly%20deteriorate%20during%20her%20stay%20at%20the%20hospital.%C2%A0Nurses%20had%20to%20restrain%20her%20because%20she%20kept%20thrashing%20in%20her%20bed%20from%20pain%2C%20before%20she%20succumbed%20to%20the%20viral%20disease%20on%C2%A0%20April%206.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20mother%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20accept%20Jamaica's%20death.%20It's%20difficult%20because%20she%20was%20taken%20from%20us%20so%20suddenly.%20She%20told%20me%20she%20couldn't%20drink%20water.%20She%20said%20she%20believed%20she%20might%20have%20rabies%20because%20she%20was%20bitten%20by%20a%20dog%20in%20February.%20I%20asked%20her%20why%20she%20didn't%20tell%20me%20right%20away.%20She%20kept%20apologising.%20I%20told%20her%20I%20wasn't%20mad%20at%20her%2C%20but%20we%20could%20have%20had%20her%20checked%20sooner.%20When%20she%20asked%20me%20if%20she%20was%20going%20to%20die%2C%20I%20felt%20scared.%20I%20wanted%20to%20go%20into%20hysterics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%20data-style%3D%5C%22news%5C%22%20data-redesign-embed%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20autopsy%20report%20showed%20she%20had%20died%20of%20rabies%20encephalitis%2C%20which%20is%20nearly%20always%20fatal%20by%20the%20time%20symptoms%20begin%20to%20appear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVillage%20authorities%20said%20the%20dog%20that%20had%20bitten%20Jamaica%20had%20also%20attacked%20seven%20other%20people%20in%20February.%20It%20was%20caught%20by%20local%20officials%20but%20died%20at%20the%20veterinary%20clinic%20eight%20days%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20tragic%20incident%2C%20the%20teen's%20family%20warned%20other%20parents%20in%20an%20online%20post%20on%20April%2018%3A%20''To%20other%20parents%2C%20be%20conscious%20if%20your%20child%20is%20acting%20strange.%20Teach%20your%20children%20to%20take%20cat%20scratches%20and%20dog%20bites%20seriously%20and%20tell%20adults%20immediately.%20Rabies%20is%20not%20a%20joke.%20It%20is%20fatal.%20Please%20do%20not%20take%20it%20lightly%2C%20so%20that%20others%20can%20avoid%20what%20my%20daughter%20experienced.%20And%20to%20pet%20owners%2C%20please%20be%20responsible%20for%20your%20animals.%20Ensure%20they%20are%20vaccinated%20so%20they%20cannot%20cause%20harm%20to%20other%20people.%20In%20spite%20of%20everything%2C%20I%20am%20proud%20of%20my%20daughter%20because%20she%20tried%20to%20be%20brave%20throughout%20the%20ordeal.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0In%20heartbreaking%20messages%20sent%20to%20her%20account%2C%20Jamaica%20chronicled%20the%20days%20before%20her%20death.She%20wrote%3A%20''Actually%2C%20I%20know%20that%20I%20have%20rabies.%20I%20just%20couldn't%20tell%20Mama%20because%20I%20didn't%20want%20her%20to%20be%20disappointed.%20That%20day%2C%20my%20mum%20thought%20I%20had%20a%20UTI.%20But%20I%20didn't%20know%20if%20it%20was%20a%20UTI%20or%20rabies.%20I've%20done%20a%20lot%20of%20research%20about%20rabies%20when%20I%20was%20bitten%20on%20February%209.%20Since%20then%2C%20I%20couldn't%20accept%20that%20I%20would%20become%20rabid%20one%20day.%20It's%20too%20late%20for%20me%20to%20be%20vaccinated.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20set%20of%20messages%20written%20on%20April%205%2C%20Jamaica%20wrote%2C%20''I%20had%20a%20hard%20time%20to%20breathe.%20I%20started%20to%20search%20on%20YouTube%20about%20rabid%20humans.%20Gosh%2C%20those%20children%E2%80%A6%20They%20will%20die%20slowly%20and%20painfully%2C%20and%20the%20hydrophobia%20they%20were%20experiencing%20is%20the%20same%20as%20mine.%20I%20can't%20believe%20a%20teenager%20like%20me%20would%20experience%20this.%20If%20I%20get%20hospitalized%2C%20please%20just%20send%20me%20into%20a%20coma%20rather%20than%20being%20conscious%20in%20pain.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713850620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-05%2Fstray-dogs-generic_650x400_71525256961.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F13-year-old-philippines-girl-hides-being-bitten-by-stray-dog-dies-of-rabies-2-months-later-5503014%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Instead%20of%20telling%20her%20parents%20the%20truth%2C%20Jamaica%20told%20them%20that%20she%20had%20scratched%20herself%20on%20metal%20wire%2C%20which%20led%20them%20to%20not%20seek%20medical%20attention.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F13-year-old-philippines-girl-hides-being-bitten-by-stray-dog-dies-of-rabies-2-months-later-5503014%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F13-year-old-philippines-girl-hides-being-bitten-by-stray-dog-dies-of-rabies-2-months-later-5503014%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F13-year-old-philippines-girl-hides-being-bitten-by-stray-dog-dies-of-rabies-2-months-later-5503014%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Godzilla%20x%20Kong%20inches%20towards%20Rs%20100%20crore%20mark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713850430000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109520697%2Cimgsize-57804.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fgodzilla-x-kong-the-new-empire-box-office-collection-rebecca-halls-film-inches-towards-rs-100-crore-mark%2Farticleshow%2F109520743.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg