staff-congress-stepped-up-ban-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%20app%20that%20uses%20less%20mobile%20data%20and%20launched%20in%20Spain%20and%20France%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20key%20draw%20to%20the%20new%20app%20is%20its%20%26quot%3BTask%20and%20Rewards%26quot%3B%20program%2C%20which%20allows%20users%2018%20or%20older%20to%20earn%20points%20by%20logging%20in%20daily%2C%20watching%20videos%2C%20liking%20posts%2C%20and%20inviting%20friends%20to%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsers%20can%20earn%20such%20points%20on%20the%20Lite%20app%20by%20watching%20videos%20for%20up%20to%2085%20minutes%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20points%20can%20be%20converted%20into%20rewards%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcoupons.businessinsider.com%2Famazon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20vouchers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Famazon-gift-card-redeem%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egift%20cards%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20TikTok%20coins%20%E2%80%94%20an%20internal%20currency%20that%20can%20be%20spent%20to%20send%20gifts%20to%20streamers%20and%20content%20creators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20commission%20said%20TikTok%20hasn't%20done%20enough%20to%20ensure%20minors%20can't%20access%20the%20rewards%20hub%2C%20and%20is%20concerned%20it%20can%20get%20kids%20addicted%20to%20the%20Lite%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20suspect%20TikTok%20'Lite'%20could%20be%20as%20toxic%20and%20addictive%20as%20cigarettes%20'light%2C'%26quot%3B%20said%20Thierry%20Breton%2C%20commissioner%20for%20the%20internal%20market%20in%20the%20EU.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20has%20until%20Wednesday%20to%20submit%20its%20defense%2C%20which%20the%20commission%20said%20it%20would%20consider%20as%20it%20seeks%20to%20suspend%20Tiktok%20Lite's%20rewards%20program%20in%20the%20EU.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20was%20also%20told%20to%20provide%20a%20risk%20assessment%20of%20its%20spinoff%20app%20by%20Tuesday.%20European%20officials%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdigital-strategy.ec.europa.eu%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fcommission-sends-request-information-tiktok-regarding-launch-tiktok-lite-france-and-spain%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20asked%20for%20it%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20be%20submitted%20by%20April%2018%2C%20saying%20that%20TikTok%20should%20have%20already%20completed%20the%20assessment%20before%20launching%20the%20Lite%20app.%20However%2C%20TikTok%20didn't%20meet%20the%20original%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnless%20TikTok%20provides%20compelling%20proof%20of%20safety%20%E2%80%94%20which%20it%20failed%20to%20do%20until%20now%E2%80%94%20we%20stand%20ready%20to%20trigger%20%23DSA%20interim%20measures%20including%20the%20%23suspension%20of%20the%20TikTokLite%20'reward%20program%2C'%26quot%3B%20Breton%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FThierryBreton%2Fstatus%2F1782414979968139392%3F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yahoo.com%2Ftech%2Feu-threatens-suspend-tiktok-lite-144644375.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%20to%20AFP%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20TikTok%20said%20the%20platform%20was%20%26quot%3Bdisappointed%20with%20this%20decision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20TikTok%20Lite%20rewards%20hub%20is%20not%20available%20to%20under%2018s%2C%20and%20there%20is%20a%20daily%20limit%20on%20video%20watch%20tasks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20said%20it%20was%20most%20concerned%20about%20the%20mental%20health%20of%20young%20TikTok%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBreton%20said%20the%20app%20provides%20%26quot%3Bendless%20streams%20of%20short%20and%20fast-paced%20videos%26quot%3B%20that%20may%20increase%20the%20risk%20of%20anxiety%2C%20depression%2C%20and%20addiction%20among%20kids%2C%20echoing%20similar%20worries%20among%20lawmakers%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20world%2C%20including%20those%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-ban-bill-explained-politics-tech-platform-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECapitol%20Hill%20mulling%20a%20TikTok%20ban%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20is%20already%20facing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fec.europa.eu%2Fcommission%2Fpresscorner%2Fdetail%2Fen%2FIP_24_926%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseparate%20set%20of%20proceedings%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20EU%20aimed%20at%20its%20main%20app%2C%20also%20based%20on%20concerns%20that%20its%20algorithm%20and%20video%20feeds%20could%20produce%20adverse%20mental%20health%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20double%20crackdown%20was%20launched%20under%20the%20European%20Union's%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdigital-strategy.ec.europa.eu%2Fen%2Fpolicies%2Fsafer-online%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDigital%20Services%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20compels%20internet%20companies%20to%20regulate%20their%20online%20content%20on%20their%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%2C%20owned%20by%20Chinese%20company%20Bytedance%2C%20is%20subject%20to%20the%20DSA's%20strictest%20rules%20because%20it's%20been%20designated%20one%20of%2022%20%26quot%3BVery%20Large%20Online%20Platforms%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20are%20classified%20as%20those%20with%20more%20than%2045%20million%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20has%20seen%20sharply%20rising%20revenues%20in%20Europe%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20with%20annual%20revenue%20increasing%20164%25%20from%20%24990%20million%20to%20%242.6%20billion%20in%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Ftiktok-hits-the-big-time-in-europe-with-huge-revenue-rise-3nfjv9czk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20its%20latest%20report%20from%20September.%3C%