m%2Ftaylor-swift-travis-kelce-relationship-timeline-photos-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKansas%20City%20Chiefs%20tight%20end%20Travis%20Kelce%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Healy%20has%20also%20moved%20on%20from%20their%20relationship.%20He%20was%20first%20linked%20to%20Gabbriette%20Bechtel%2C%20a%20model%2C%20in%20September%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20everything%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20Healy%20and%20Bechtel's%20apparent%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBechtel%20is%20a%20model%20and%20musician%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.highsnobiety.com%2Fp%2Fgabbriette-interview%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHighsnobiety%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20Bechtel%20(whose%20given%20name%20is%20Gabriella)%20was%20born%20in%20Orange%20County%2C%20California%2C%20in%20July%201997%2C%20to%20parents%20of%20Mexican%20and%20German%20ancestry.%20Bechtel%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vogue.com%2Farticle%2Fmodel-chef-gabbriette-bechtel%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVogue%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20as%20a%20child%2C%20she%20wanted%20to%20become%20a%20professional%20ballerina%2C%20but%20ended%20up%20dancing%20in%20music%20videos%20when%20she%20moved%20to%20Los%20Angeles.%20From%20there%2C%20she%20launched%20a%20career%20as%20a%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Vogue%2C%20Bechtel%20has%20appeared%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20campaigns%20for%20brands%20including%20Heaven%20By%20Marc%20Jacobs%20and%20Skims.%20She%20also%20walked%20the%20runway%20for%20Diesel's%20autumn%2Fwinter%202023%20fashion%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20modeling%2C%20Bechtel%20also%20makes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC23MEa8PoAL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link%26igsh%3DMzRlODBiNWFlZA%3D%3D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecooking%20content%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20she%20posts%20on%20Instagram.%20She%20told%20Vogue%20that%20her%20parents%20influenced%20her%20love%20of%20cooking.%3C%2Fp%3