ll%20the%20time.%20It%20ended%20too%20abruptly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHealy%20and%20Bechtel%20were%20first%20linked%20in%20New%20York%20in%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Fthe-1975-matty-healy-model-gabbriette-bechtel-kiss-new-york-city-7966289%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeople%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20photos%20of%20Healy%20and%20Bechtel%20kissing%20in%20SoHo%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20publication%20reported%20that%20their%20connection%20was%20unclear%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20that%20they%20both%20had%20a%20mutual%20friend%20in%20Charli%20XCX.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pair%20have%20been%20quiet%20about%20their%20speculated%20relationship%2C%20and%20haven't%20explicitly%20confirmed%20it.%20However%2C%20Healy's%20mother%20once%20interacted%20with%20Bechtel%20on%20Instagram%20after%20Bechtel%20posted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCyl6MvUvae4%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ephoto%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20herself%20in%20a%20thong%20and%20a%20leather%20apron%20from%20her%20collaboration%20with%20R%26amp%3BM%20Leathers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20exactly%20how%20I%20hope%20to%20look%20in%20mine%20when%20it%20arrives!!%26quot%3B%20Healy's%20mother%2C%20Denise%20Welch%2C%20replied%2C%20accompanied%20by%20three%20thumbs%20up%20and%20heart%20emoji.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBechtel%20also%20made%20a%20cameo%20on%20Welch's%20Instagram%20account%2C%20appearing%20in%20a%20photo%20with%20Welch%2C%20Healy%2C%20and%20his%20younger%20brother%20Louis.%20The%20three%20saw%20Welch's%20play%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Gap%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20she%20wrote%20in%20the%20caption%20of%20the%20post%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Blovely%20to%20have%20the%20family%20in%20to%20see%20mum%20at%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type