espan%20and%20plan%20for%20the%20worst.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere's%20no%20easy%20answer%20to%20earning%20more%20money%2C%20but%20it's%20important%20to%20not%20ignore%20that%20factor.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20encourage%20my%20clients%20to%20focus%20less%20on%20frugality%20and%20more%20on%20how%20they'll%20invest%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcfp%5C%22%3Ecertified%20financial%20planner%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20my%20goal%20is%20to%20help%20self-made%20professionals%20build%20wealth%20that%20they%20can%20enjoy%20throughout%20their%20lives.%20To%20do%20that%2C%20we%20have%20to%20make%20sure%20their%20money%20will%20last%20throughout%20their%20lifetimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20we%20also%20need%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20clients%20actually%20have%20opportunities%20to%20use%20their%20money%20%3Cem%3Enow%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0while%20they're%20young%2C%20healthy%2C%20and%20able%20to%20fully%20experience%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20process%20we%20use%20to%20build%20long-term%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ffinancial-plan%5C%22%3Efinancial%20plans%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20work%2C%20including%20what%20your%20investment%20strategy%20should%20consider%20and%20why%20living%20frugally%20is%20a%20poor%20strategy%20for%20getting%20rich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20Plan%20for%20change%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20goals%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fretirement-planning%5C%22%3Eretirement%20planning%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20probably%20evolve%20over%20time.%20The%20person%20you%20are%20today%20will%20not%20be%20the%20same%20person%20who%20retires%20in%2010%2C%2020%2C%20or%2030%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20long-term%20financial%20plan%20that%20works%20accounts%20for%20inevitable%20shifts%20in%20goals%2C%20values%2C%20priorities%2C%20and%20circumstances.%20Although%20you%20might%20not%20know%20exactly%20%3Cem%3Ewhat%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewill%20change%2C%20you%20can%20still%20plan%20for%20an%20evolving%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20save%20more%20than%20you%20think%20you%20need%20to%20when%20you%20can.%20If%20you%20find%20you%20have%20excess%20cash%20flow%2C%20don't%20default%20to%20spending%20it%20or%20upgrading%20your%20lifestyle.%20Direct%20that%20money%20to%20investments%20instead%20so%20you%20can%20grow%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAvoid%20unrealistic%20assumptions%20about%20future%20income%20and%20expenses.%20For%20my%20own%20planning%2C%20I%20assume%20a%20lower-than-expected%20growth%20in%20income%20and%20a%20higher-than-expected%20run%20rate%20for%20my%20cost%20of%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20making%20decisions%2C%20opt%20for%20choices%20that%20allow%20you%20to%20walk%20away%20at%20a%20low%20cost.%20This%20makes%20it%20possible%20to%20change%20or%20adjust%20course%20as%20needed.%20Be%20cautious%20about%20decisions%20that%20demand%20fixed%20commitments%20(like%20buying%20a%20house)%20that%20are%20difficult%20to%20reverse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20Look%20for%20ways%20to%20earn%20more%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPersonally%2C%20I've%20shifted%20from%20%26quot%3Bretire%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%26quot%3B%20to%20a%20more%20balanced%20approach%20to%20my%20financial%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20save%20less%20money%20now%20because%20I%20want%20to%20use%20some%20of%20my%20income%20for%20important%20experiences%20throughout%20life.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20save%20%3Cem%3Eeverything%20%3C%2Fem%3Efor%20use%20on%20a%20distant%20(and%20unreliable!)%20%26quot%3Bsomeday%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20financial%20plan%20can%20accommodate%20this%20choice%20for%20two%20main%20reasons%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20I%20saved%20aggressively%20when%20I%20could%20for%20almost%20a%20decade.%20I've%20saved%20at%20least%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbeyondyourhammock.com%2Fpercent-of-income-saved%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E30%25%20to%2040%25%20of%20my%20income%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20fact%20I%20did%20so%20in%20the%20past%20gives%20me%20increased%20flexibility%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20and%20energy%20into%20earning%20more%20money%20through%20growing%20my%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20grow%20wealth%2C%20increasing%20your%20income%20will%20fast-track%20your%20efforts.%20Too%20many%20people%20who%20want%20to%20throw%20out%20money%20tips%20ignore%20this%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20understand%20why%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20talk%20about%20it.%20Earning%20more%20is%20not%20easy%20to%20do%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20one%20piece%20of%20prescriptive%20advice%20to%20give%20that%20will%20help%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20we%20cannot%20ignore%20the%20importance%20of%20making%20more%20money%20if%20our%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20more%20wealth.%20There%20are%20many%20avenues%20that%20can%20get%20you%20to%20a%20higher%20income%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20need%20one%20right%20answer.%20You%20need%20to%20select%20and%20stick%20with%20a%20strategy%20that%20makes%20sense%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E3.%20Remember%2C%20frugality%20will%20only%20get%20you%20so%20far%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20what%20you%20want%20to%20do%2C%20you'll%20need%20money%20to%20afford%20your%20chosen%20lifestyle%20in%20the%20future.%20And%20you%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20work%20to%20earn%20an%20income%20forever.%20By%20choice%20or%20by%20circumstance%2C%20you%20will%20eventually%20need%20another%20way%20to%20pay%20for%20your%20needs%20other%20than%20your%20own%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20we%20must%20recognize%20the%20necessity%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-save-money%5C%22%3Esaving%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%5C%22%3Einvesting%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There's%20no%20disputing%20that.%20The%20question%20is%20%3Cem%3Ehow%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20frugally%20to%20get%20wealthy%20is%20possible%3B%20it's%20a%20simple%20fact%20that%20the%20lower%20your%20expenses%20are%2C%20the%20more%20you%20can%20save.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20an%20inefficient%20path%20to%20building%20wealth.%20There%20are%20only%20so%20many%20costs%20you%20can%20cut.%20And%20%3Cem%3Eonly%20%3C%2Fem%3Esaving%20money%20misses%20out%20on%20opportunities%20to%20create%20assets%20that%20increase%20in%20value%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E4.%20Develop%20an%20investment%20strategy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20grow%20wealth%20without%20pinching%20pennies%2C%20you%20have%20to%20invest%20%E2%80%94%20and%20you%20have%20to%20do%20that%20wisely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20sound%20investment%20strategy%20needs%20to%20consider%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWhat%20investment%20vehicles%20to%20use%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20right%20asset%20allocation%20based%20on%20your%20goals%20and%20your%20time%20horizons%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20expenses%20associated%20with%20your%20chosen%20investments%20and%20how%20that%20may%20impact%20your%20returns%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%20data-stringify-border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20data-stringify-indent%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20leverage%20diversification%20across%20your%20portfolio%20as%20well%20as%20across%20the%20specific%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-online-brokerage%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-online-brokerage%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3Ebrokerage%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0or%20assets%20you%20invest%20into%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20tax%20implications%20of%20your%20choices%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMistakes%20to%20avoid%2C%20including%20speculating%2C%20market%20timing%2C%20and%20taking%20on%20too%20much%20(or%20the%20wrong%20type)%20of%20risk%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20just%20scratches%20