0I%20wasn't%20expecting%20it%20to%20happen%20so%20fast.%20We%20were%20delighted%2C%20although%20I%20had%20to%20go%20to%20every%20doctor's%20appointment%20on%20my%20own%20because%20of%20the%20shutdown%20for%20COVID-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20staff%20member%20videoed%20my%2012-week%20ultrasound%20so%20Greg%20could%20feel%20more%20involved.%20It%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20happy%20day.%20But%20it%20was%20horrible.%20They%20couldn't%20detect%20a%20heartbeat.%20I%20needed%20a%20D%26amp%3BC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20extensive%20genetic%20testing%20before%20the%20next%20round%20of%20IVF.%20The%20geneticists%20discovered%20that%20I%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmy.clevelandclinic.org%2Fhealth%2Fdiseases%2F15200-turner-syndrome%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMosaic%20Turner%20syndrome%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20chromosomal%20condition%20that%20occurs%20randomly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20shocked.%20Typically%2C%20those%20with%20Mosaic%20Turner%20syndrome%20are%20short.%20I'm%205ft%209in%20tall.%20However%2C%20the%20disorder%20was%20linked%20to%20major%20fertility%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fer-doctor-how-to-prevent-scary-heart-condition-aortic-dissection-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheart%20problems%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20mom%20holding%20her%20baby%20with%20a.fireplace%20behind%20them.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6626be090dfb1341e9fdbcb3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22576%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJaclyn%20Feiberg%20with%20her%20three-month-old%20baby%2C%20Emersyn.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jaclyn%20Feiberg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20later%20diagnosed%20with%20endometriosis%20and%20had%20multiple%20procedures%20in%202022.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20traumatic%20things%20was%20having%20one%20of%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-its-possible-to-get-pregnant-without-fallopian-tubes-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efallopian%20tubes%3C%2Fa%3E%20removed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20we%20did%20a%20total%20of%20six%20more%20rounds%20of%20IVF%2C%20costing%20more%20than%20%2450%2C000.%20I%20was%20having%20constant%20injections.%20We%20got%20our%20hopes%20up%20twice.%20But%2C%20first%2C%20it%20was%20a%20chemical%20pregnancy%20and%20then%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fcan-stress-cause-a-miscarriage%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearly%20miscarriage%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20a%20huge%20toll%20mentally.%20It%20affected%20our%20marriage.%20Greg%20works%20as%20a%20firefighter.%20He's%20a%20fixer%2C%20but%20he%20couldn't%20do%20anything%20to%20fix%20this%20for%20me%20%E2%80%94%20and%20for%20us.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20should%20stop%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me%20at%20one%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20trying%20to%20protect%20me%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20the%20right%20answer.%20Traveling%20and%20getting%20another%20dog%20wasn't%20going%20to%20fulfill%20our%20desire%20to%20have%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20began%20to%20think%20about%20donor%20eggs%20from%20a%20stranger.%20But%20we're%20a%20very%20close%20family%20%E2%80%94%20Stephanie%2C%20Meredith%2C%20and%20my%20youngest%20sister%2C%20Samantha%2C%20lived%20through%20every%20high%20and%20low%20of%20our%20IVF%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20sisters'%20selflessness%20made%20our%20dreams%20come%20true%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20wanted%20to%20help%20in%20any%20way%20they%20could.%20The%20genetic%20piece%20was%20important%20to%20me.%20Meredith%2C%20a%20mom%20of%20twins%2C%20put%20herself%20forward%20as%20our%20donor.%20Stephanie%2C%20who%20has%20two%20kids%2C%20and%20Samantha%20did%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20ruled%20out%20Samantha%20because%20she%20didn't%20already%20have%20children.%20Our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.c