0and%C2%A0%20how%20to%20give%20him%20a%20balanced%20diet.%20Our%20anxiety%20increases%20when%20we%20see%20a%20variety%20of%20opinions%20from%20different%20doctors%20and%20nutritionists.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20numbers%20don%E2%80%99t%20lie%20and%20the%20rising%20obesity%20amongst%20children%20today%20underscores%20the%20need%20for%20the%20right%20nutrition%20for%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20era%20of%20quick%20commerce%20and%20fast%20food%2C%20one%20might%20be%20tempted%20to%20buy%20packaged%20food%20and%20purees%20like%20cerelac%20for%20babies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20new%20report%20has%20unearthed%20shocking%20facts.%20A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.publiceye.ch%2Fen%2Fmedia-corner%2Fpress-releases%2Fdetail%2Fsugar-for-nestle-not-all-babies-are-equal%5C%22%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20by%20the%20Swiss%20organisation%20Public%20Eye%2C%20and%20the%20International%20Baby%20Food%20Action%20Network%20(IBFAN)%2C%20found%20that%20Nestle%2C%20the%20Swiss%20multinational%20food%20company%2C%20adds%20more%20sugar%20in%20infant%20food%20products%20in%20lower-income%20countries%2C%20including%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20states%20that%20its%20infant%20cereal%20Cerelac%2C%20intended%20for%20babies%20from%20the%20age%20of%206%20months%2C%20contained%202.7%20grams%20of%20added%20sugar%20per%20serving%20in%20India.%20The%20same%20Cerelac%20contains%20no%20added%20sugar%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20Germany.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20is%20this%20important%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20seeing%20a%20rising%20trend%20in%20childhood%20obesity%2C%20with%2043%20lakh%20children%20in%20the%200-5%20age%20group%20identified%20as%20obese%20or%20overweight%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20recommends%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310976%2Fharsha-vardhan-bengaluru-starts-lil-goodness-healthy-snack-brand-nutrition-booster%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20added%20sugars%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20sweetening%20agents%20should%20be%20used%20in%20food%20for%20children%20under%20the%20age%20of%20three%20to%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20obesity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPackaged%20food%20items%20like%20Cerelac%20typically%20provide%20an%20easy%20option%20for%20parents%20and%20have%20been%20used%20for%20decades%20in%20India.%20Over%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20doctors%20have%20stopped%20recommending%20such%20cereals%20and%20instead%20ask%20parents%20to%20provide%20homemade%20healthier%20alternatives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20do%20you%20offer%20your%20babies%20when%20they%20start%20solids%3B%20and%20later%2C%20to%20your%20picky%20toddlers%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20spoke%20to%20paediatricians%20and%20nutritionists%20to%20answer%20these%20burning%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhich%20solid%20food%20should%20you%20introduce%20first%20to%20your%20baby%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%20things%20first%2C%20you%20must%20start%20solids%20for%20your%20baby%20only%20at%20six%20months%20of%20age%20and%20not%20earlier%2C%20say%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20start%20solids%2C%20breast%20milk%20or%20formula%20remains%20the%20primary%20source%20of%20nutrition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20is%20to%20let%20babies%20try%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20foods%20slowly%20and%20introduce%20them%20to%20varied%20tastes.%20Start%20with%20single%20ingredients%20and%20give%20each%20food%20item%20for%20three%20days.%20You%20could%20give%20carrots%2C%20apples%2C%20bananas%20or%C2%A0%20papayas%20in%20pureed%20and%20mash%20forms.%20You%20can%20slowly%20introduce%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.