C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENo%20screens%20while%20eating%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Vikram%20Gagneja%2C%20the%20Head%20of%20Department%2C%20Paediatrics%20And%20PICU%20(Paediatric%20Intensive%20Care%20Unit)%2C%20Manipal%20Hospital%2C%20Dwarka%2C%20says%20that%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20to%20model%20healthy%20eating%20habits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhenever%20we%20eat%20at%20hotels%2C%20we%20notice%20children%20eating%20with%20a%20video%20playing%20in%20front%20of%20them.%20This%20is%20a%20potentially%20harmful%20habit%2C%20explains%20Dr%20Gagneja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChildren%20see%20us%20as%20role%20models.%20We%20need%20to%20stop%20eating%20in%20front%20of%20a%20screen%20and%20stop%20feeding%20children%20by%20distracting%20them%20using%20a%20TV%20or%20a%20mobile%20phone.%20They%20should%20see%20what%20food%20they%20are%20eating%20and%20develop%20an%20interest%20in%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20we%20model%20good%20behaviour%2C%20we%20need%20to%20model%20good%20eating%20habits%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENo%20added%20sugar%20till%202%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEveryone%20accepts%20that%20completely%20restricting%20sugar%20is%20not%20possible%2C%20but%20experts%20recommend%20using%20natural%20sugars%20and%20sweeteners%20instead.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20see%20so%20many%20obese%20children%20now.%20Sugar%20is%20extremely%20addictive%2C%20and%20if%20introduced%20at%20a%20young%20age%2C%20children%20don%E2%80%99t%20eat%20anything%20else.%20Fruits%20have%20natural%20sugars%20and%20can%20be%20used%20to%20sweeten%20porridge.%20Refined%20sugar%20is%20not%20advisable%2C%20completely%20avoid%20till%20one%2C%20and%20after%20that%2C%20you%20can%20use%20dates%20and%20jaggery%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Gagneja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20one%20year%20of%20age%2C%20no%20sugar%20and%20salt%20should%20be%20given%20to%20babies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3