number%20plates%20for%20cars%20and%20bikes%2C%20which%20led%20me%20to%20experiment%20with%20custom%20letter%20shapes.%20I%E2%80%99d%20offer%20this%20service%20to%20my%20friends%20and%20family%20for%20free%20just%20so%20I%20could%20see%20my%20lettering%20being%20used.%20This%20was%20my%20unintended%20first%20step%20into%20public%20typography%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20unassuming%2040-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F98296%2Findian-type-foundry-satya-rajpurohit%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESatya%20co-founded%20Indian%20Type%20Foundry%3C%2Fa%3E%20(ITF)%20in%202009%20in%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20ITF%20with%20just%20one%20font%20family%20(Fedra%20Hindi).%20Since%20then%2C%20we%20have%20produced%20over%20450%20font%20families%2C%20including%20300%20retail%20font%20families%20available%20for%20licensing%20and%20around%20150%20custom%20and%20open-source%20fonts.%20Some%20of%20our%20most%20popular%20fonts%20are%20Kohinoor%2C%20Volte%2C%20Akhand%2C%20Poppins%2C%20Satoshi%2C%20General%20Sans%2C%20Swatzer%2C%20Teko%2C%20and%20Hind%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETransforming%20typographic%20landscape%20with%20Indian%20languages%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20clocks%20an%20annual%20revenue%20of%20close%20to%20USD%202%20million%20(Rs%2016.48%20crore%20approximately)%20and%20has%20around%20300%20clients%20from%20Fortune%20500%20companies.%20Among%20its%20clients%20are%20giants%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20Apple%2C%20Google%2C%20Samsung%2C%20Sony%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Hyundai%2C%20Unilever%2C%20Tata%20Play%2C%20Star%20Sports%2C%20SBI%2C%20Zee%20TV%2C%20Mahindra%2C%20Disney%2C%20Kotak%2C%20Discovery%2C%20and%20Aaj%20Tak.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20Satya%20received%20the%20prestigious%20%E2%80%98SoTA%20Catalyst%20Award%E2%80%99%20presented%20by%20the%20Society%20of%20Typographic%20Aficionados.%20He%20has%20been%C2%A0featured%C2%A0in%20Fortune%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9840%20Under%2040%E2%80%99%20list%20for%20three%20consecutive%20years%20(2016%2C%202017%20and%202018).%20In%202017%2C%20he%20was%20also%20on%20GQ%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9850%20Most%20Influential%20Young%20Indians%E2%80%99%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20ITF%20is%20recognised%20as%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20type%20foundries%20globally%2C%20having%20developed%20fonts%20for%20non-Indian%20languages%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Thai%2C%20Cyrillic%20(Russian)%2C%20Greek%2C%20Hebrew%2C%20Sinhalese%20and%20Korean.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20what%20makes%20ITF%20special%20is%20its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F45907%2Findian-languages-hindi-bengali-sanskrit-dravidian-kannada-malayalam-tamil-telugu-urdu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efocus%20on%20Indian%20languages%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAkhand-Multiscript_11zon-1713535979-500x500.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Akhand%20multiscript%20by%20ITF%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAkhand-Multiscript_11zon-1713535979-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAkhand-Multiscript_11zon-1713535979-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAkhand-Multiscript_11zon-1713535979-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAkhand-Multiscript_11zon-1713535979-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAkhand-Multiscript_11zon-1713535979-1536x1536.jpg%201536w%