as%E2%80%99%20in%20Indian%20languages%20add%20to%20the%20complexity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20cannot%20imagine%20a%20single%20day%20not%20thinking%20about%20fonts%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatya%E2%80%99s%20parents%20wanted%20him%20to%20become%20a%20doctor%3B%20so%20he%20spent%20two%20years%20in%20Kota%20but%20failed%20to%20clear%20the%20exams.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20he%20decided%20to%20pursue%20his%20interest%20in%20art%20instead.%20He%20joined%20Chandigarh%20College%20of%20Fine%20Arts%2C%20and%20while%20studying%20there%2C%20he%20learned%20about%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Design%20(NID)%2C%20Ahmedabad.%20He%20then%20secured%20admission%20to%20the%20prestigious%20design%20institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20two%20years%20at%20Kota%20were%20the%20worst%20of%20my%20life.%20I%20was%20not%20a%20good%20student%20at%20school%20except%20in%20art.%20Even%20if%20I%20had%20cleared%20the%20medical%20exams%20and%20become%20a%20doctor%2C%20I%20would%20have%20been%20a%20terrible%20doctor%20because%20it%20was%20not%20something%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Satya%20with%20a%20rueful%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202407px)%20100vw%2C%202407px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIndic-fonts_11zon-1713536047.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222407%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Indic%20fonts%20by%20ITF%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIndic-fonts_11zon-1713536047.jpg%202407w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIndic-fonts_11zon-1713536047-300x192.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIndic-fonts_11zon-1713536047-500x320.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIndic-fonts_11zon-1713536047-768x492.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIndic-fonts_11zon-1713536047-1536x984.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIndic-fonts_11zon-1713536047-2048x1312.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIndic-fonts_11zon-1713536047-150x96.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347881%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221542%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIndic%20fonts%20by%20ITF%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20NID%2C%20he%20got%20interested%20in%20motion%20graphics%2C%20one%20application%20of%20which%20is%20creating%20titles%20and%20credits%20for%20films.%20However%2C%20here%20serendipity%20played%20a%20key%20role.%20He%20%E2%80%9Cstumbled%20upon%20an%20unexpected%20opportunity%E2%80%9D%20in%20his%20third%20year%20%E2%80%94%20an%20internship%20in%20type%20design%20at%20Linotype%2C%20the%20pioneer%20in%20making%20high-quality%20typefaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20experience%20was%20transformative.%20In%20those%20three%20months%2C%20I%20delved%20into%20the%20world%20of%20typography%2C%20gaining%20an%20understanding%20of%20its%20significance%20and%20intricacies.%20The%20experience%20ignited%20my%20passion%20for%20type%20design%20and%20reshaped%20my%20career%20trajectory%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Satya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20internships%20at%20Linotype%20in%20Germany%20and%20Dalton%20Maag%20in%20the%20UK%20were%20pivotal%20in%20preparing%20him%20to%20set%20up%20his%20own%20venture.%20They%20taught%20him%20the%20crucial%20blend%20of%20precision%20and%20creativity%20needed%20in%20type%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20cannot%20imagine%20a%20single%20day%20not%20thinking%20about%20fonts.%20A%20font%20is%20a%20collection%20of%20letters%2C%20numbers%20and%20symbols%2C%20all%20dressed%20up%20in%20a%20certain%20style.%20When%20I%20design%20fonts%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20like%20I%E2%80%99m%20designing%20outfits%20for%20words%20so%20they%20can%20express%20different%20emotions%20and%20ideas%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Satya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFonts%20have%20long-term%20value.%20For%20instance%2C%20Helvetica%20was%20first%20published%20in%201957%2C%20yet%20this%20font%20remains%20relevant%20even%20today.%20ITF%20develops%20both%20traditional%20fonts%20(used%20for%20text%20in%20books%20and%20newspapers)%20and%20experimental%20or%20display%20fonts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraditional%20fonts%2C%20such%20as%20Times%20New%20Roman%20and%20Arial%2C%20prioritise%20readability%20and%20versatility.%20In%20contrast%2C%20experimental%20fonts%20go%20beyond%20functionality%20and%20embrace%20innovative%20shapes%2C%20concepts%20and%20designs.%20These%20fonts%20prioritise%20artistic%20expression%20and%20invigorate%20visual%20design.%20They%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20character%20and%20are%20used%20in%20headlines%2C%20logos%20and%20posters.%20For%20sports%20events%2C%20children%E2%80%99s%20books%2C%20and%20film%20posters%2C%20%E2%80%98grunge%E2%80%99%20(messy%20text)%20is%20used%20at%20times%2C%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FMaking-a-presentation_11zon-1713536103.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Satya%20making%20a%20presentation%20about%20the%20various%20Indian%20language%20fonts%20by%20ITF.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FMaking-a-presentation_11zon-1713536103.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FMaking-a-presentation_11zon-1713536103-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FMaking-a-presentation_11zon-1713536103-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2F