0space%20for%20daughters%20of%20sex%20workers%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKranti%20started%20its%20work%20at%20Kamathipura%2C%20known%20as%20the%20red%20light%20area%20in%202011%20for%20daughters%20of%20sex%20workers%20and%20survivors%20of%20trafficking.%20Children%20here%20often%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20access%20to%20a%20good%20education%20and%20opportunities%20to%20build%20a%20better%20life.%20Kranti%20removes%20this%20stigma%20associated%20with%20being%20the%20child%20of%20a%20sex%20worker%20and%20empowers%20these%20young%20girls%20to%20achieve%20their%20full%20potential%2C%20unburdening%20them%20from%20years%20of%20societal%20conditioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20Sandhya%E2%80%99s%20example.%20From%20being%20a%20child%20who%20hated%20going%20to%20school%2C%20she%20is%20today%20pursuing%20an%20MA%20in%20gender%20and%20peacebuilding%20at%20the%20University%20for%20Peace%20in%20Costa%20Rica.%20Sandhya%20is%20one%20of%20the%20many%20girls%20from%20Kranti%20who%20are%20pursuing%20their%20postgraduate%20studies%20in%20foreign%20universities%2C%20and%20working%20on%20bringing%20about%20social%20change%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20girls%20like%20them%20in%20brothels%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20was%20bullied%20for%20my%20dark-coloured%20skin%20and%20mother%E2%80%99s%20profession%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandhya%E2%80%99s%20mother%20had%20big%20dreams%20for%20her%20daughter.%20She%20wanted%20Sandhya%20to%20be%20educated%20in%20a%20private%20school%20and%20left%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20trying%20to%20get%20her%20admitted%20into%20one.%20But%20there%20was%20a%20problem%3A%20if%20she%20disclosed%20her%20profession%2C%20no%20school%20would%20admit%20Sandhya%2C%20so%20her%20mother%20chose%20to%20instead%20say%20that%20she%20worked%20as%20a%20domestic%20help.%20In%20that%20sense%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.the