ther%20saying%20that%20her%20daughter%20was%20a%20wrestling%20coach%20at%20the%20Special%20Areas%20Games%20(SAG)%20centre%20run%20by%20the%20Sports%20Authority%20of%20India%20(SAI)%20in%20the%20Khuman%20Lampak%20area%20of%20Imphal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20their%20conversation%2C%20my%20mother%20talked%20about%20losing%20her%20husband%20and%20the%20financial%20struggles%20at%20home.%20My%20mother%20also%20said%20that%20she%20had%20three%20sons%2C%20and%20if%20her%20%5Belderly%20lady%E2%80%99s%5D%20daughter%20could%20coach%20one%20of%20them%2C%20she%20would%20be%20very%20grateful.%20Soon%2C%20a%20wrestling%20coach%20visited%20our%20home%2C%20took%20a%20look%20at%20me%20and%20agreed%20to%20coach%20me.%20I%20started%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263525%2Fanshu-malik-first-indian-woman-world-wrestling-championship-winner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraining%20in%20wrestling%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20I%20was%20about%2012%20or%2013%20at%20the%20SAG%20centre%20in%20Khuman%20Lampak%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20struggling%20for%20a%20year%2C%20he%20developed%20a%20good%20understanding%20of%20wrestling%20and%20began%20competing%20in%20different%20age%20groups%20representing%20Manipur%20in%20regional%20tournaments.%20Chungreng%20aimed%20to%20one%20day%20represent%20India%20in%20the%20Olympics.%20Meanwhile%2C%20his%20mother%20was%20working%20in%20the%20fields%20back%20home%2C%20barely%20earning%20Rs%20150%20to%20Rs%20200%20a%20day%2C%20and%20his%20elder%20brothers%20found%20work%20operating%20JCBs%20far%20away%20up%20in%20the%20hills.%20Education%20was%20a%20luxury%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20money%20to%20come%20back%20home%20and%20visit%20my%20family.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20money%20to%20travel%20for%20tournaments.%20There%20were%20times%20I%20would%20borrow%20money%20from%20my%20friends%20with%20a%20promise%20to%20return%20it.%20Despite%20getting%20selected%20to%20compete%20in%20national%20tournaments%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20money%20to%20travel.%20I%20remember%20juniors%20training%20with%20me%2C%20would%20talk%20behind%20my%20back%20saying%20that%20I%20was%20poor.%20I%20had%20aspirations%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261513%2Fpooja-rani-boxing-tokyo-olympics-sports-hero-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompeting%20in%20the%20Olympics%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20despite%20progressing%20well%2C%20poverty%20came%20in%20the%20way.%20Whenever%20I%20think%20of%20these%20times%2C%20I%20start%20to%20cry%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls%20with%20tears%20flowing%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20wrestling%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20Chungreng%20decided%20that%20his%20time%20was%20better-spent%20farming%2C%20working%20as%20a%20farm%20hand%20on%20rice%20fields%20and%20supporting%20the%20family.%20By%20the%20middle%20of%202012%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20quit%20wrestling%20altogether%2C%20fell%20in%20love%2C%20got%20married%2C%20and%20went%20back%20home.%20About%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20later%2C%20his%20first%20child%20was%20born%2C%20and%20life%20seemed%20destined%20to%20go%20in%20a%20certain%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201032px)%20100vw%2C%201032px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0017-1713276448.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manipur%20MMA%20Representative%20Chungreng%20Koren%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0017-1713276448.jpg%201032w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0017-1713276448-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen